<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>国土报最新头条</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Sat, 25 Nov 2023 00:30:34 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>以色列人无法停止观看哈马斯暴行的视频。后果是毁灭性的</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-25/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/israelis-cant-stop-watching-videos-of-hamas-atrocities-the-consequences-are-ruinous/0000018c-0382-dca2-a9fd-678a2d4b0000</link><description>由于强烈、成瘾地观看通过社交媒体和短信传播的残酷图像，以色列人正在出现创伤后应激障碍 (PTSD) 症状</description><pubDate>Fri, 24 Nov 2023 23:46:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-25/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/israelis-cant-stop-watching-videos-of-hamas-atrocities-the-consequences-are-ruinous/0000018c-0382-dca2-a9fd-678a2d4b0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列领导人必须告诉我们战争的最后一天</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-25/ty-article-opinion/.premium/israels-leaders-must-tell-us-about-the-wars-last-day/0000018c-0331-de3d-af9e-0bf713060000</link><description></description><pubDate>Fri, 24 Nov 2023 22:26:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-25/ty-article-opinion/.premium/israels-leaders-must-tell-us-about-the-wars-last-day/0000018c-0331-de3d-af9e-0bf713060000</guid></item><item><title>10月7日之前一年多，以色列军队洞察了哈马斯袭击以色列城镇、以色列国防军基地的计划</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-24/ty-article-magazine/.premium/over-a-year-before-october-7-israels-army-had-insight-into-hamas-attack-plan/0000018c-02a2-de3d-af9e-0bf7901b0000</link><description>该组织多年前就开始准备从加沙发起进攻，但以色列的分析仍然有误。袭击发生前两个月，一名军士警告说，噩梦般的场景现在可能会发生，但她被忽视了</description><pubDate>Fri, 24 Nov 2023 20:55:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-24/ty-article-magazine/.premium/over-a-year-before-october-7-israels-army-had-insight-into-hamas-attack-plan/0000018c-02a2-de3d-af9e-0bf7901b0000</guid></item><item><title>“虚假指控”：以色列在访问期间受到批评后召见西班牙和比利时大使</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2023-11-24/ty-article/israel-summons-spanish-belgian-ambassadors-following-criticism-during-visit-to-rafah/0000018c-02fa-d4d0-addf-47fe9ef60000</link><description>这一消息是在西班牙和比利时领导人批评以色列在加沙行动中给平民造成的苦难之后宣布的。以色列指责两人“没有将危害人类罪的全部责任归咎于哈马斯”</description><pubDate>Fri, 24 Nov 2023 20:51:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2023-11-24/ty-article/israel-summons-spanish-belgian-ambassadors-following-criticism-during-visit-to-rafah/0000018c-02fa-d4d0-addf-47fe9ef60000</guid></item><item><title>至少10名泰国哈马斯扣押的人质被释放回以色列</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-24/ty-article/at-least-10-thai-hamas-held-hostages-released-back-to-israel/0000018c-02d8-dca2-a9fd-67da2eea0000</link><description>泰国没有公布被绑架者的姓名或状况，但感谢卡塔尔、以色列、埃及、伊朗、马来西亚和红十字会。获取有关泰国人质既往病史的医疗信息比以色列人质更棘手</description><pubDate>Fri, 24 Nov 2023 19:53:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-24/ty-article/at-least-10-thai-hamas-held-hostages-released-back-to-israel/0000018c-02d8-dca2-a9fd-67da2eea0000</guid></item><item><title>这些是周五从哈马斯囚禁中获释的以色列妇女和儿童</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-24/ty-article/these-are-the-israeli-women-and-children-freed-from-hamas-captivity-on-friday/0000018c-0178-d4d0-addf-47febba50000</link><description>49天前，在哈马斯袭击期间，以色列人质在加沙附近的基布兹被绑架，并被拖入飞地，作为加沙战争期间有限停火协议的一部分，这些人质被释放</description><pubDate>Fri, 24 Nov 2023 17:21:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-24/ty-article/these-are-the-israeli-women-and-children-freed-from-hamas-captivity-on-friday/0000018c-0178-d4d0-addf-47febba50000</guid></item><item><title>为什么以色列人如此反对与哈马斯的战争停火？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-24/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/why-are-israelis-so-averse-to-a-cease-fire-in-the-war-with-hamas/0000018c-01f0-d12e-a1fc-71f5ccdc0000</link><description>与普遍观点相反，停止枪击的协议在战场之外发挥着重要作用。难怪政府和军队都想方设法避免它</description><pubDate>Fri, 24 Nov 2023 16:25:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-24/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/why-are-israelis-so-averse-to-a-cease-fire-in-the-war-with-hamas/0000018c-01f0-d12e-a1fc-71f5ccdc0000</guid></item><item><title>为什么这位种族冲突问题顶级专家对以色列人和巴勒斯坦人抱有希望</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-24/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/why-this-top-expert-on-ethnic-conflicts-has-hope-for-israelis-and-palestinians/0000018c-0191-dca2-a9fd-659bf8590000</link><description>世界民族政治冲突权威社会学家、政治哲学家安德烈亚斯·维默 (Andreas Wimmer) 表示，赢得战争的方法是征服敌人，但结束冲突的方法是让对手分享权力地位</description><pubDate>Fri, 24 Nov 2023 15:26:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-24/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/why-this-top-expert-on-ethnic-conflicts-has-hope-for-israelis-and-palestinians/0000018c-0191-dca2-a9fd-659bf8590000</guid></item><item><title>加沙停火满足了伊朗和美国利益的融合</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2023-11-24/ty-article/.premium/the-cease-fire-in-gaza-feeds-a-confluence-of-iranian-and-american-interests/0000018c-00e1-de0a-a18e-06f5e9d90000</link><description>伊朗和美国都明白，加沙战争 — — 尤其是以色列和黎巴嫩边境的冲突 — — 可能会将整个地区拖入一场战争，迫使两国直接交战。对伊朗而言，停火可能是恢复现状的机会</description><pubDate>Fri, 24 Nov 2023 11:54:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2023-11-24/ty-article/.premium/the-cease-fire-in-gaza-feeds-a-confluence-of-iranian-and-american-interests/0000018c-00e1-de0a-a18e-06f5e9d90000</guid></item><item><title>随着加沙领导人掌权，哈马斯海外官员认为权力减弱</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2023-11-24/ty-article/.premium/hamas-officials-abroad-see-power-wane-as-gazan-leaders-take-control/0000018c-00ce-d99b-a7ee-1dde271f0000</link><description>最近在卡塔尔会见哈马斯领导人伊斯梅尔·哈尼亚和其他高级官员的阿拉伯外交官表示，每一项有关该组织未来或人质交易的提议或讨论都会得到这样的答案：“我们将看看他们在加沙说什么”</description><pubDate>Fri, 24 Nov 2023 10:59:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2023-11-24/ty-article/.premium/hamas-officials-abroad-see-power-wane-as-gazan-leaders-take-control/0000018c-00ce-d99b-a7ee-1dde271f0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列边境沿线的居民全副武装，焦虑不安，正在为最坏的情况做好准备</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-24/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/armed-and-anxious-residents-along-israels-borders-are-bracing-for-the-worst/0000018b-ff81-de73-a9bb-ffe781fb0000</link><description>战争爆发以来，以色列边境居民的安全感受到严重动摇。曾经享受平静生活和田园风光的人们现在正在武装自己，想知道敌人需要多长时间才能突破脆弱的栅栏</description><pubDate>Fri, 24 Nov 2023 05:17:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-24/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/armed-and-anxious-residents-along-israels-borders-are-bracing-for-the-worst/0000018b-ff81-de73-a9bb-ffe781fb0000</guid></item><item><title>13 名以色列人质从哈马斯手中获释；加沙停火生效 以色列释放39名巴勒斯坦囚犯</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-24/ty-article-live/cease-fire-set-to-begin-at-7-a-m-13-women-and-children-to-be-released-in-afternoon/0000018b-ff7f-d4d0-addf-ffffa24a0000</link><description>第一批被哈马斯扣押的以色列人质抵达以色列 ■ 为期四天的停火于当地时间周五上午 7 点生效 ■ 卡塔尔-埃及与哈马斯达成的单独调解协议中释放了 11 名人质 ■ 人质协议中释放了 39 名巴勒斯坦被拘留者抵达约旦河西岸检查站 ■ 拜登：今天只是开始，我们预计明天将有更多人质获释，后天还会有更多人质 ■ 载有人道主义援助物资的卡车通过与埃及接壤的拉法过境点进入加沙地带 ■ 至少 1,200 名平民和士兵自 10 月 7 日以来，以色列境内有 236 名人质在加沙地带被扣押 ■ 哈马斯控制的卫生部：加沙有 14,854 人死亡</description><pubDate>Fri, 24 Nov 2023 04:11:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-24/ty-article-live/cease-fire-set-to-begin-at-7-a-m-13-women-and-children-to-be-released-in-afternoon/0000018b-ff7f-d4d0-addf-ffffa24a0000</guid></item><item><title>随着以色列进入加沙休战，内塔尼亚胡继续对国防机构发动战争</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-24/ty-article/.premium/as-israel-heads-into-gaza-truce-netanyahu-keeps-waging-war-on-the-defense-establishment/0000018b-fdd8-de73-a9bb-ffff98840000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡知道以色列国防军将因摧毁加沙而获得赞誉，就像他明白人质交易将帮助他走出政治深渊一样。与此同时，极右翼分子伊塔马尔·本-格维尔正在制定一项退出执政联盟的战略</description><pubDate>Fri, 24 Nov 2023 04:02:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-24/ty-article/.premium/as-israel-heads-into-gaza-truce-netanyahu-keeps-waging-war-on-the-defense-establishment/0000018b-fdd8-de73-a9bb-ffff98840000</guid></item><item><title>随着第一批人质即将获释，以色列已经在计划下一阶段的加沙战争</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-24/ty-article/.premium/israel-planning-for-stage-2-of-the-war-against-hamas-even-before-the-hostages-are-home/0000018b-fd9a-d99b-a7eb-fd9e53d40000</link><description>战斗暂停将使以色列国防军能够在加沙地带南部组织新的进攻——这可能需要几个月的时间。受西岸局势困扰 ■</description><pubDate>Fri, 24 Nov 2023 04:01:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-24/ty-article/.premium/israel-planning-for-stage-2-of-the-war-against-hamas-even-before-the-hostages-are-home/0000018b-fd9a-d99b-a7eb-fd9e53d40000</guid></item><item><title>国土报卡通</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/daily-cartoon/2023-11-24/ty-article-opinion/haaretz-cartoon/0000018b-fe51-d99b-a7eb-ffd7c5750000</link><description></description><pubDate>Thu, 23 Nov 2023 22:35:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/daily-cartoon/2023-11-24/ty-article-opinion/haaretz-cartoon/0000018b-fe51-d99b-a7eb-ffd7c5750000</guid></item><item><title>为了所有以色列人的利益，废除排他性民族国家法</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-23/ty-article-opinion/.premium/repeal-the-exclusionary-nation-state-law-for-the-sake-of-all-israelis/0000018b-fdd9-de73-a9bb-ffff291b0000</link><description></description><pubDate>Thu, 23 Nov 2023 21:41:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-23/ty-article-opinion/.premium/repeal-the-exclusionary-nation-state-law-for-the-sake-of-all-israelis/0000018b-fdd9-de73-a9bb-ffff291b0000</guid></item><item><title>感谢以色列极右翼财政部长，我们正处于经济灾难的边缘</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/